name: MapProxy OSM Switzerland
description: MapProxy is an open source proxy for geospatial data. It caches, accelerates and transforms data from existing map services (e.g., OpenStreetMap Switzerland) and serves any desktop or web GIS. This service provides access to OSM-based map tiles and geospatial data for Switzerland.
data_themes: Inspire themes, Geospatial data, Map tiles, Base maps
